title: Interbank Deposits, Weekly Reporting Member Banks for New York, NY
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Four Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1920-1935 (2)--Original Data, 1934-1942 (3)--Original Data, 1942-1947 (4)--Original Data, 1946-1949. Data Are Reported By All Banks As Gross Figures. Data Are For All Interbank Deposits -- Demand, Domestic And Foreign Plus Time, Domestic And Foreign. Source: Federal Reserve Board, Data For 1934-1941: Banking And Monetary Statistics. Data For 1942: Federal Reserve Bulletin.

This NBER data series m14139b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 14 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter14.html.
